@CBP just made the largest fentanyl drug bust in #USA history at a legal port of entry. 

Over 600 pounds of drugs hidden inside vegetables were driven into a checkpoint full of armed police and drug dogs. 

Tell me again how a wall will stop this?

Day 8:
@SpeakerRyan,

#Dreamers are students studying to be our next trailblazers; they’re teachers working hard to unlock potential in our kids.

Let’s include the #DreamAct or #USAact in the omnibus so they can stay in the only country they know.

Sincerely,
@RepLujanGrishampic.twitter.com/qyYKHGwv2y – at United States Capitol Building
